title: evaluating fields of a product type
pid: 779f3e03-fe1a-472a-93e2-083d596be376
body: |2-
  /home/jeff〉ls | each { |it| $"($it.name) is ($it.size)" }
  ╭────┬─────────────────────────╮
  │  0 │ Desktop is 4.0 KiB      │
  │  1 │ Documents is 4.0 KiB    │
  │  2 │ Downloads is 4.0 KiB    │
  ...
